176
00:11:36,259 --> 00:11:39,239
Then shop until you're happy.

177
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:42,800
I will take this bag.

178
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:47,280
I'm sorry, Miss Jing. Someone has reserved this bag.

179
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:54,960
Sure enough, it's bad luck to be with you. I can't even buy the bag I want.

180
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,819
Let's go then.

181
00:11:56,819 --> 00:11:59,149
