182
00:12:09,210 --> 00:12:13,835
I can bring you along. You'll have to pay for my services as a tour guide.

183
00:12:15,090 --> 00:12:19,609
Sure. I'll pay for today's expenses.

184
00:12:19,609 --> 00:12:22,350
I'm hungry. Let's eat.

185
00:12:23,330 --> 00:12:25,729
Please come again.

186
00:12:29,351 --> 00:12:32,329
I will have this steak and a pizza.

187
00:12:32,329 --> 00:12:34,879
I want this one, this one, and this one.

188
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:37,200
You ordered so many. Can you finish them all?

189
00:12:39,490 --> 00:12:41,800
Help me to announce it.

190
00:12:43,380 --> 00:12:47,619
Ladies and gentlemen, this lady said she's paying for your meals.

191
00:12:48,300 --> 00:12:51,051
Thank you.

192
00:12:54,450 --> 00:12:55,620
Here.

193
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:57,599
Eat first.

194
00:12:57,599 --> 00:12:58,920
Where are we going after this?

195
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:01,119
Do you still want to follow me?

196
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:10,000
- Where are we going?
- I want to go to the washroom.

197
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:13,679
Do you want to go there while holding hands like high school girls?

198
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:19,499
What's wrong?

199
00:13:19,499 --> 00:13:22,099
Hey, are you okay?

200
00:13:22,099 --> 00:13:23,460
- What's wrong?
- Open your eyes.

201
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:25,619
Don't come close. Give him some air.

202
00:13:25,619 --> 00:13:27,339
Do you hear that? Don't come too close. Thank you.

203
00:13:27,339 --> 00:13:29,999
- Move away.
- I think he has a heart attack. Did you bring his medicine?

204
00:13:29,999 --> 00:13:32,919
No, we only came out for a meal.

205
00:13:32,919 --> 00:13:37,310
Are you a doctor? If you're not, you'll be responsible if anything happens. It has nothing to do with our restaurant.

206
00:13:37,310 --> 00:13:38,719
Stop pinning the blame on others when she's trying to save his life.

207
00:13:38,719 --> 00:13:41,979
Even if anything happens, it's a problem with the service and dishes of your restaurant.

208
00:13:41,979 --> 00:13:44,399
Don't just stand here. Call an ambulance!

209
00:13:58,010 --> 00:14:00,160
He's waking up.

210
00:14:02,455 --> 00:14:05,470
He's waking up. He's awake.

211
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:06,880
He's waking up.

212
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:09,219
He's waking up.

213
00:14:09,219 --> 00:14:10,995
Slowly.

214
00:14:10,995 --> 00:14:14,099
He should be okay.

215
00:14:14,099 --> 00:14:15,419
This way.

216
00:14:15,419 --> 00:14:17,799
- Step aside, please.
- Hurry.

217
00:14:17,799 --> 00:14:19,659
Give me a hand.

218
00:14:21,020 --> 00:14:23,639
Thank you.

219
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,579
Are you okay?

220
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:48,679
Did you know

221
00:14:48,679 --> 00:14:50,499
that my dad died suddenly

222
00:14:50,499 --> 00:14:52,880
all alone in the middle of the night in an empty restaurant

223
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:54,799
