253
00:17:48,280 --> 00:17:50,039
I learned it.

254
00:18:03,730 --> 00:18:05,949
Just now...

255
00:18:05,949 --> 00:18:08,049
What about just now?

256
00:18:12,910 --> 00:18:15,789
Nothing. I'll get off first.

257
00:18:27,570 --> 00:18:28,990
Are you sure you don't want to go to the hospital?

258
00:18:28,990 --> 00:18:30,530
