260
00:18:33,130 --> 00:18:35,790
the doctor said my heart palpitations are caused by low blood sugar

261
00:18:35,790 --> 00:18:38,709
so my hands tremble and I feel dizzy.

262
00:18:39,839 --> 00:18:41,700
[Mo Ziqi]

263
00:18:43,350 --> 00:18:46,929
It's okay, do your work. I can go up by myself.

264
00:18:46,929 --> 00:18:48,966
Take care then.

265
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:30,029
- Yes, Old Mo.
- Xiao Fu, did you run into something tricky there?

266
00:19:30,029 --> 00:19:32,569
Lin is back. He knows that woman is leaving.

267
00:19:32,569 --> 00:19:34,509
He tried to hurt himself.

268
00:19:34,509 --> 00:19:36,509
I can only try my best to keep Jing Zhixia

269
00:19:36,509 --> 00:19:37,989
to keep Lin under control.

270
00:19:37,989 --> 00:19:40,329
I'll finish the meeting in Japan ahead of schedule.

271
00:19:40,329 --> 00:19:42,789
I'll return this weekend to do a checkup on you.

272
00:19:42,789 --> 00:19:45,039
Okay. I...

273
00:19:57,145 --> 00:19:59,884
What does Fu Zeyi mean by this?

274
00:19:59,884 --> 00:20:01,499
Have we met before?

275
00:20:01,499 --> 00:20:04,022
Aizhe needs to pay off all its debts within a week.

276
00:20:04,022 --> 00:20:06,741
Or else, Fu Group will sue you.

277
00:20:10,090 --> 00:20:13,210
Fu Zeyi, what are you doing here?

278
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:14,150
You're drunk.

279
00:20:14,150 --> 00:20:16,189
Let's go. I'll take you home.

280
00:20:24,850 --> 00:20:27,129
I can't fall asleep at all.

281
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:44,939
Oh, no. I'm even hallucinating now.

282
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:02,580
Are you better now?

283
00:21:02,580 --> 00:21:04,999
I've gone crazy.

284
00:21:04,999 --> 00:21:07,759
I can even hear him now.

285
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:34,220
Fu Zeyi, what exactly do you want?

286
00:21:34,220 --> 00:21:36,100
Why can't you let me live in peace?

287
00:21:36,100 --> 00:21:38,490
I'm going to make him explain tomorrow.

288
00:21:38,490 --> 00:21:41,520
[Aizhe Hotel]

289
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:43,319
[Aizhe Hotel]

290
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:47,679
Hello, Director Jing.

291
00:21:47,679 --> 00:21:50,589
Sister, you're early.

292
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:54,019
Is Fu Zeyi here? I need to see him.

293
00:21:54,019 --> 00:21:56,419
What did he do to you again?

294
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:59,209
Wait a minute.

295
00:21:59,209 --> 00:22:02,150
Was he the one who tortured you like this?

296
00:22:02,150 --> 00:22:03,909
Come with me.

297
00:22:07,730 --> 00:22:09,949
He didn't torture me.

298
00:22:09,949 --> 00:22:11,809
Wait.

299
00:22:11,809 --> 00:22:15,089
It was your day off yesterday.

300
00:22:15,089 --> 00:22:16,890
Did he still cling to you and torment you?

301
00:22:16,890 --> 00:22:19,609
I'll seek justice for you now.

302
00:22:20,390 --> 00:22:22,290
He didn't torture me.

303
00:22:22,290 --> 00:22:24,469
Then what happened?

304
00:22:25,730 --> 00:22:30,469
Don't tell me he hit you.

305
00:22:47,130 --> 00:22:49,369
He didn't hit me.

306
00:22:49,369 --> 00:22:51,569
Then what happened?

307
00:22:52,870 --> 00:22:54,170
We almost kissed.

308
00:22:54,170 --> 00:22:57,309
What? You almost kissed?

309
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:06,870
If we hadn't been interrupted, we would've kissed.

310
00:23:06,870 --> 00:23:09,289
But we didn't kiss.

311
00:23:12,190 --> 00:23:16,529
Things don't seem certain between the two of you so what's going on here?

312
00:23:19,670 --> 00:23:22,929
Yes. I must not repeat my old mistake

313
00:23:22,929 --> 00:23:25,209
and let him take advantage of me...

314
00:23:25,209 --> 00:23:27,529
again.

315
00:23:27,529 --> 00:23:30,189
I'll ask for his explanation now.

316
00:23:30,189 --> 00:23:31,829
Let's go.

317
00:23:35,870 --> 00:23:37,650
Wait.

318
00:23:37,650 --> 00:23:39,350
Who's that?

319
00:23:41,990 --> 00:23:43,609
Hello?

320
00:23:43,609 --> 00:23:46,141
Why do you want to see me?

321
00:23:47,083 --> 00:23:48,910
Miss Jing, I'm sorry

322
00:23:48,910 --> 00:23:52,589
that I didn't know you were Aizhe's Director Jing.

323
00:23:52,589 --> 00:23:54,409
No need to apologize.

324
00:23:54,409 --> 00:23:55,970
Why did you want to see me?

325
00:23:55,970 --> 00:23:58,789
Then I'll be straightforward.

326
00:23:59,950 --> 00:24:04,429
I want to buy your remaining shares of Aizhe Hotel.

327
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:06,890
Why should I sell my shares to you?

328
00:24:06,890 --> 00:24:10,769
I can offer three times the price.

329
00:24:11,530 --> 00:24:15,250
It's not about money. My dad left the hotel to me.

330
00:24:15,250 --> 00:24:17,789
I have sentimental value for the hotel.

331
00:24:17,789 --> 00:24:19,639
Sentimental value?

332
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:25,699
Then why did you sell your shares to Fu Zeyi?

333
00:24:26,846 --> 00:24:28,246
What did you say?

334
00:24:28,246 --> 00:24:30,336
Your reaction...

335
00:24:30,336 --> 00:24:32,329
Didn't you know about this?

336
00:24:32,329 --> 00:24:36,670
He acquired your shares to obtain the land the hotel was on.

337
00:24:36,670 --> 00:24:41,809
He plans to demolish the hotel to build Fu's business district there.

338
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:46,439
I called earlier to ask about the sale of shares.

339
00:24:46,439 --> 00:24:49,679
Miss Jing, it's a pleasure working with you.

340
00:24:49,679 --> 00:24:51,640
Miss Jing trusts me now.

341
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,479
Then I'll wait for your good news.

342
00:24:53,479 --> 00:24:57,119
The Fu Group's business district will be built near Aizhe Hotel.
[Fu Group's Business District Blueprint]

343
00:24:57,119 --> 00:24:59,639
I don't see Aizhe Hotel on the map.

344
00:25:02,620 --> 00:25:05,059
You can keep on dreaming.

345
00:25:08,290 --> 00:25:10,749
I won't let you touch Aizhe Hotel.

346
00:25:14,090 --> 00:25:17,269
So should we contact other minor shareholders?

347
00:25:18,990 --> 00:25:21,509
We'll just wait and watch the show.

348
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:34,519
Get out of my way.

349
00:25:37,948 --> 00:25:39,750
[Fu Group's Business District Blueprint]

350
00:25:54,340 --> 00:25:58,260
No wonder Aizhe Hotel is not on the map. You are planning to demolish it.

351
00:25:59,875 --> 00:26:01,834
You found out.

352
00:26:01,834 --> 00:26:05,339
Why? Did you not want me to find out?

353
00:26:05,339 --> 00:26:08,219
If your second uncle didn't come to me to buy my shares today,

354
00:26:08,219 --> 00:26:10,580
I would've been kept in the dark.

355
00:26:10,580 --> 00:26:13,379
My second uncle came to you to buy your shares?

356
00:26:15,280 --> 00:26:18,539
Didn't you acquire my shares as well?

357
00:26:19,180 --> 00:26:22,979
What an elaborate trap, Director Fu.

358
00:26:22,979 --> 00:26:25,740
You suppressed me in the name of compensation.

359
00:26:25,740 --> 00:26:28,959
Then you forced me to sell my shares at a low price.

360
00:26:28,959 --> 00:26:31,572
It's all to demolish this hotel

361
00:26:31,572 --> 00:26:34,219
to build Fu's business district.

362
00:26:35,260 --> 00:26:38,950
Since everything had gone according to your plan,

363
00:26:38,950 --> 00:26:40,590
why...

364
00:26:41,187 --> 00:26:44,606
Why did you have to keep a loser like me here?

365
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:55,550
Do you need a loser like me

366
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:57,399
to celebrate your victory,

367
00:26:57,399 --> 00:26:59,720
or are you punishing me?

368
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:04,719
You want to punish me so I can watch the hotel my father had built ruined in my hands.

369
00:27:04,719 --> 00:27:07,581
All that for your trap to be perfect?

370
00:27:09,860 --> 00:27:11,759
I thought we could...

371
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:31,279
Being ruthless is your true self, right?

372
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:36,619
It's all your conspiracy, isn't it?

373
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:44,399
I'll never let you get your way, Fu Zeyi.

374
00:27:58,240 --> 00:28:01,039
Have you ever played the piano before?

375
00:28:01,039 --> 00:28:02,579
No.

376
00:28:02,579 --> 00:28:04,259
It's all right.

377
00:28:04,259 --> 00:28:08,970
Today, our first lesson is about how to recognize the notes.

378
00:28:08,970 --> 00:28:11,139
No.

379
00:28:11,139 --> 00:28:14,034
Then what about learning "Twinkle, Twinkle Little Star"?

380
00:28:14,034 --> 00:28:16,250
No.

381
00:28:16,250 --> 00:28:19,029
Then what would you like to learn, Mr. Fu?

382
00:28:19,029 --> 00:28:21,449
I want to learn the song I sent you.

383
00:28:21,449 --> 00:28:25,379
No problem. I'll play it right away.

384
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:45,240
01, 53,

385
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:47,540
27, 49,

386
00:28:47,540 --> 00:28:49,419
36.

387
00:28:51,360 --> 00:28:53,080
One more time.

388
00:28:53,080 --> 00:28:54,710
Okay.

389
00:28:59,780 --> 00:29:01,539
One more time.

390
00:29:02,378 --> 00:29:04,175
One more time.

391
00:29:47,975 --> 00:29:54,875
♫  There's not a day that I'm afraid of being alone  ♫

392
00:29:55,825 --> 00:30:02,265
♫  I’m afraid of seeing you again after we said our goodbyes  ♫

393
00:30:03,395 --> 00:30:10,324
♫  I'm slowly getting used to missing you  ♫

394
00:30:10,324 --> 00:30:17,085
♫  It seems like I've locked my heart away as the memory lingers  ♫

395
00:30:17,085 --> 00:30:24,855
♫  If I decide to be brave this time,  ♫

396
00:30:24,855 --> 00:30:31,470
♫  Then I'll hold your hands till eternity  ♫

397
00:30:32,445 --> 00:30:39,405
♫  The moment we found the emotions we'd lost,  ♫

398
00:30:39,405 --> 00:30:45,635
♫  It will overcome those lonely moments little by little  ♫

399
00:30:49,905 --> 00:30:53,390
♫  If you were by my side,  ♫

400
00:30:53,390 --> 00:30:58,135
♫  No matter how many promises we've broken  ♫

401
00:30:58,135 --> 00:31:01,385
♫  There's nothing I'm not willing to do  ♫

402
00:31:01,385 --> 00:31:04,935
♫  in order to have a simple and ordinary life with you  ♫

403
00:31:04,935 --> 00:31:08,330
♫  If you were by my side,  ♫

404
00:31:08,330 --> 00:31:14,940
♫  All my regrets will be blown away by the wind  ♫

405
00:31:14,940 --> 00:31:21,645
♫  I only want you to be with me every second, every minute  ♫
